Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.87,0:00:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算知道事實
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.47,0:00:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但為了保命我只能閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.34,0:00:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是這樣，如果那個冒牌貨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.98,0:00:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能好好治理國家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.98,0:00:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也算是一種選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.15,0:00:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我都快走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.35,0:00:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.29,0:00:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持有“蒼天的青玉”的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.76,0:00:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是這溫德布倫\N真正的女王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.70,0:00:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這笑話真是惡劣透頂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.64,0:00:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.34,0:00:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表演時間開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.68,0:00:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了照相機啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.38,0:00:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以賣不少錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.98,0:00:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳可以早一步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始乙HiME的畢業典禮啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.18,0:01:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到夢想了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.55,0:01:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心悸動無法平息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.46,0:01:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶物誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.09,0:01:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿盈內心 開始散放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.24,0:01:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何會如此不安呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法控制的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.58,0:02:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人不禁落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.02,0:02:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有朝一日一定會抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算中途受挫也不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.23,0:02:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣向前邁進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能踏出小小的一步 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嶄新的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.58,0:02:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第15話 愛莉卡，哭泣\N不…不要，別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳安分一點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.86,0:02:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝爾蓋…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼們，到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薛…凱？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螞蟻？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.27,0:03:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.47,0:03:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，幹掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一發會打中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是很注重地盤觀念的\N橫條紋團
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這附近亂搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.44,0:03:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螞蟻，妳還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇壞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.42,0:03:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.77,0:04:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茱麗葉姊姊\N給他們老樣子的水刑處罰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙已經不是初犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就照平常的兩倍下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.68,0:04:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.41,0:04:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從被抓的姑娘身上也撈一筆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼謝爾蓋老頭會？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.19,0:04:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也是既笨，運氣又不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到外號\N“北方獵犬”的你竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝爾蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從妳嘴巴裡面聽到好話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.17,0:05:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我哪有一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.74,0:05:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只聽過妳講壞話喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是螞蟻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會著涼的，穿上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散一下步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種地方我再也不…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.13,0:06:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也同學，開門
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也·克羅榭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.34,0:07:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還做了真不得了的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼老是這樣接二連三的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼天的青玉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以靜留姊姊才…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.53,0:07:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼，真是沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.15,0:07:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧我還讓妳負責我的房間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是錯看妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是妳在背後給她捲捲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳才是剛好有機會當上三和弦\N就想趁機表現一下是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪可能有這種事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是覺得很麻煩耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說千繪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼妳會在那裡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.08,0:08:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當年在這應考時認識的朋友\N有事情找我談
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的行情還是這麼好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.35,0:08:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳才是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.65,0:08:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道？要不要撈撈看河底呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.83,0:08:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太讚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.23,0:08:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳喜歡真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.44,0:08:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看…看著這種東西\N就會覺得好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科學好像魔法一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.31,0:08:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我們的祖先
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還居住在叫做地球的星球上時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.95,0:08:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有更了不起的科學技術呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更了不起？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以想像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，大家一定過得很幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.63,0:09:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.03,0:09:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我知道那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是燈塔吧？婆婆有說過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.37,0:09:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆的婆婆的\N更久之前的婆婆的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.88,0:09:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青之星成為路標
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.88,0:09:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引導吾與吾所愛之公主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越過上千星球…上萬夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.26,0:09:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往即將來臨的黃金未來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒聽過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最早來到這個星球的船員\N流傳下來的詩歌其中一段
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引導的青之星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼天的青玉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.36,0:10:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是得到夢想\N還有戀情的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀情…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.07,0:10:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝爾蓋…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安，這是個美妙的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:11:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，起床，妮娜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.45,0:11:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手，昨天很晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不～行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起床起床
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,0:11:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳回來了呢，愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，開始早晨的掃除工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們搶第一個吧，Let's GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.97,0:11:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還Let's Go咧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.17,0:11:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳昨晚到底上哪…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來妳總算回來啦，愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.79,0:11:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千繪學姊，早安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事找妳，可以來一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.54,0:12:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已經承認\N妳入學後沒多久的制服一案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.68,0:12:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有健行考試的意外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.85,0:12:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及這次的事情都是自己幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了我一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是制服不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健行考試的時候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們的裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有被動過手腳的跡象
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是沒有證據
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能隨便把惡作劇行為鬧大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.77,0:12:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於這點，我向妳們道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是她一個人幹的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一連串的行為很惡劣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.58,0:12:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要身為被害者的各位舉發
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.95,0:12:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可透過懲罰委員會進行處分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.19,0:12:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒意見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…沒有這個意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不介意嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過原來是美也啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全沒發現呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有種出乎意料的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會難得，居然這麼天真
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的想要實現\N成為乙HiME的夢想的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就應該趁早\N多清除一個對手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.39,0:13:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其像妳這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.26,0:13:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.93,0:13:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼吵鬧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉亞女士，學園長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於美也·克羅榭的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經無須討論
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.75,0:13:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.65,0:13:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受理她的退學申請了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監護人也正式提出申請
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.69,0:13:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以看她難以升學\N和今後母國的情勢並不安穩為由
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:13:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想退學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去送她一程
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.50,0:14:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺真不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.62,0:14:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想妳應該會介意…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛…愛莉卡，妳沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子妳比想像中還沒神經\N這樣我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.97,0:14:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟父親有約
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不，沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.61,0:14:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢走～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:14:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳昨晚跟…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王少校…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉，我也得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,補課…不，那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我趕時間，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以借點時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開會就開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飯就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人外找就趕走他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啦，真白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:15:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說妳一直窩在房間裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.38,0:16:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.58,0:16:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟妳無關
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷淡喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.75,0:16:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟真白原則上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.45,0:16:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有著契約關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.29,0:16:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不過是形式上而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.40,0:16:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實也這麼認為吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為我根本就不夠格當王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來發生這種事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可也是很努力在做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.94,0:16:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個沒禮貌的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不過是對他好一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就爬到我頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.45,0:16:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃，難道真白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳對巧海頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.25,0:16:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我怎麼可能\N迷上那種人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是一時鬼迷心竅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳自己說了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.93,0:16:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳再多嘴我可不管妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.70,0:16:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且妳怎麼可能瞭解\N男女之間的情感嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.84,0:17:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.21,0:17:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼戀愛一類的，我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…唉呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.22,0:17:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…妳也對誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真容易到手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳說成為乙HiME\N是好不容易找到的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.55,0:17:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為要花多少功夫\N才能攻陷妳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高潔端正可愛的乙HiME？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笑死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣\N像妳這種小鬼才傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點反彈都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.07,0:18:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.94,0:18:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.08,0:18:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，妳說她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.34,0:18:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，蕾娜成就夢想\N也得到戀情是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.02,0:18:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她選擇戀情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.62,0:18:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了生小孩而捨棄乙HiME身份
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此無法保護國王和王妃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至連自己都保護不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.19,0:18:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲慘地死去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.60,0:18:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最討厭你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…為什麼對那種人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨…笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是妳哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可也一直忍耐著耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳哭成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.95,0:18:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡…妳這…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.52,0:18:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千繪，謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急事？是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個計劃總算要開始執行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以關於那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你儘快找出真正的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了實現我們的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.34,0:19:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都需要正牌公主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不過問方法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到之後就當作我們的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.35,0:19:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用上你得意的\N床上功夫也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…我會…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太愚蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她跟妮娜同年耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.07,0:20:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還不是蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那個人的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前正在建造\N我的新城堡圖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.05,0:20:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以注入活力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.45,0:20:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是頂端這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.62,0:20:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，妳很沒品味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.26,0:20:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像真白的風格，這樣也好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要與這座城一同重生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.07,0:20:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，要加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來比賽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看是我先成為Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是真白先當上女王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.31,0:21:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經是女王了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.02,0:21:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能成為讓大家幸福的女王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.36,0:21:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，來比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.63,0:21:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼現在開始畢業紀念舞鬥\N代表選拔會第一戰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.10,0:21:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代表有兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.57,0:21:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被選上的人可以無條件升上珍珠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.77,0:21:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請謹記這點參戰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.24,0:21:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准輸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是餞別禮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.33,0:21:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.63,0:21:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會忘記妳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.81,0:22:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.89,0:22:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇氣會實現願望 Do your best
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.06,0:22:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.83,0:22:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只等著我的故事 現在開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.81,0:22:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其逃避 不如挺身面對更好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.62,0:22:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是少女的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.79,0:22:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很努力唷\N就算內心突然感到寂寞的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.33,0:22:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要以笑容面對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.27,0:23:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼NO NO NO 你的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.24,0:23:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有快樂的未來 我想守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.51,0:23:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.68,0:23:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄的心意 比寶石更耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.09,0:23:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出自信向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.09,0:23:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.71,0:23:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，妳的對象是誰？\N（這是約定喔！）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.98,0:23:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能說出去喔
