Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.92,0:23:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到是迫水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.45,0:23:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦！
